Interface LongStack

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Stack<java.lang.Long>
    All Known Implementing Classes:

    public interface LongStack
extends Stack<java.lang.Long>
    A type-specific Stack; provides some additional methods that use polymorphism to avoid (un)boxing.
